ape consisting of four or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"vertices, specified as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the edges that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use a polygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"building, a lake, or an area you want to highlight."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNPolygon","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolygon","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShape/geoJSONDataUsingEncoding:":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape\/geoJSONDataUsingEncoding:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns the GeoJSON string representation of the shape encapsulated in a data"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object."}],"title":"geoJSONDataUsingEncoding:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshape\/geojsondatausingencoding:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"geoJSONDataUsingEncoding:","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"geoJSONDataUsingEncoding:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolygon":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","type":"reference"},{"text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"polygons that do not overlap. For example, you could use a multipolygon shape","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to represent the body of land that consists of an island surrounded by an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"atoll: the inner island would be one ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","type":"reference"},{"text":" object, while the surrounding","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"atoll would be another. You could also use a multipolygon shape to represent a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"group of disconnected but related buildings.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPolygon","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNMultiPolygon","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/objc(pl)NSSecureCoding":{"type":"unresolvable","title":"NSSecureCoding","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/objc(pl)NSSecureCoding"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNVectorStyleLayer/predicate":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnvectorstylelayer\/predicate","title":"predicate","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer\/predicate","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The style layer’s predicate."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"predicate"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointAnnotation":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation","title":"MLNPointAnnotation","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPointAnnotation"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointannotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a one-dimensional shape located at a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single geographical coordinate. Depending on how it is used, an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object is known as a point annotation or point shape. For"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"example, you could use a point shape to represent a city at low zoom levels, an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"address at high zoom levels, or the location of a long press gesture."}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeCollectionFeature":{"kind":"s